WHAT IS ACM SERVICE IN AWS? it stand for amazon certificate manager , it is just making ur websit secure for user
it is just an encripted certificate we can plug on our website 
- search for acm 
- click on certificate manager
- click on request certificate
- click public then next
- put ur website domain name
- select DNS validation - recommended
- select RSA 2048
- click on request 
# how to validate the certificate
- click on the created certificate
- click on creat record twice
